message.body: Hi I'm at work but I miss you. I was moving all weekend it sucked are you better

It was horrible but I am blacking it out and trying to enjoy my new iPhone;)
I decided I needed it for cali ya know
iPhone that's exciting! Fun. Are you back in w-chester or elsewhere?
No I'm staying at Wendy's;) it's amazing. Can we get together soon when are you free

I'm still borderline but I want to see you. Maybe we could have tea or something?
